Jure Pelko (born May 17, 1990) is a Slovenian professional basketball player for Helios Suns of the Slovenian League. He is a 1.90 m tall combo guard.


== Professional career ==
In August 2016, he signed a one-year deal with Union Olimpija.On June 21, 2017, he signed a two-years deal with Helios Suns.


